					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220702023750/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/Zac">Zacharias</a></li>
					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220702023750/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/Mal">Malachias</a></li>
					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220702023750/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/1_Mac">1 Machabees</a></li>
